/ flash is cleared with each request. This means that valuesstored there will only 
/ be available in the next request.

- if flash.any?
	- flash.each do |name, msg|
		- if msg.is_a?(String)
			%div{class: "alert alert-#{name.to_s == 'notice' ? 'notice' : 'alert'}" }
				= content_tag :p, msg, :id => "flash_#{name}"